Neymar may have missed his Brazil side's hapless exit from their home World Cup, but he's wasted no time in raising the stakes.

The Barcelona star posted one of his trademark selfies on his Instagram account of him and his friends playing poker.

Neymar was ruled out of his country's final two matches after injuring his back in the quarter-final against Colombia.

